      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares the volute-plus-impeller topology with the CPB device under assessment. Operating conditions in the validation set (3–5 L/min, 2500–3500 RPM) bracket the COU operating envelope. The Giersiepen hemolysis model and Lagrangian particle-tracking methodology are identical between validation and COU simulations."
