      "rationale": "At MRL 2 with a commercially validated solver and demonstrated iterative convergence (residuals < 1×10⁻⁵, QoI change < 0.1% over final 200 iterations), explicit solver error quantification beyond code verification is not required. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for MRL 2."
