      "rationale": "k-ω SST turbulence model selected based on FDA nozzle benchmark performance (VR-04) and published literature for rotating blood-contacting devices. Sensitivity to turbulence model (k-ω SST vs. realizable k-ε) < 3% on pressure head. Giersiepen hemolysis model validated against Wurzinger (1985) experimental hemolysis data for physiological shear rates."
