    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for a Class II device at MRL 2. Pressure-head validation error (4.1% mean, 6.8% maximum) is well within the ±10% acceptance band. The worst-case RH of 0.93 at 5 L/min / 3500 RPM satisfies the RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion. The credibility assessment supports acceptance of the CFD model for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
